### Event Details

**Event Name:** HackInTheBox (HITB)  
**Organizers:** D4rkm4tter & Kampf  
**Website:** [HackInTheBox at SAINTCON](https://saintcon.org/evt-hackinthebox/)  

#### Description
HITB is an evening hacker space located near the event venue, open after the main speaking tracks and conference have closed. It offers accommodations for soldering, presentations, networking, and contest collaboration. The event has been held since 2016 and provides a safe space for conference attendees and community members.

#### Hours of Operation
- **Tuesday:** 6:00 PM – 11:59 PM
- **Wednesday:** 6:00 PM – 11:59 PM
- **Thursday:** 6:00 PM – 11:59 PM

**Location:** The Hyatt Hotel, across the street.

#### Additional Information
- HITB is recognized as one of the best hangout spots after-hours during SAINTCON.
- It is not an official event of SAINTCON but has been assisted by them.

